      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEAR ELIZA (1) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 488m behind Blue Denim (29.32) in a Grade 6. Boasts two wins from three starts out of this box. Has winning claims on her best figures. JUST A JOKER (3) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest when checked in the run and finishing third in a Grade 6 at this track (28.73). Harder here but will be in this for a long way. ZIPPING SEATTLE (2) collided in the run and missed the frame when fifth (29.27) at this track over 488m in a Grade 6. Has the ability and looks a key chance. MYSTIC PIXEL (8) is a last-start placegetter when at the top of betting - in the mix again.",
